Teltoli
--------

In her sleep, she hears Carnages message and Cyber Claw asking anyone if there was CR Chambers anywhere. She cracks open one eyes from where she lay on the floor in beast mode, and sees Cyber Claw, looking like Dinobot, enter the hallway she is in. She points a paw in the direction.

"Over there, and take the first hall on the left" She yawns, putting a paw across her mouth. "Scuse me"

Teltoli then hears Grimlock's com about help, and she stands up, ruffling her wings. She races out the door and takes flight, seeing Carnage down below. She waves, grinning, and then sets off to the direction of Grimlock.

She reaches it rougly 5 minutes later, being a fast flyer, and sees the Autoguns pop out. Teltoli also sees a huge missile being fired at him, and her eyes widen (OOC: No I'm not moding, that was posted). The missile was huge! She dips her wings and dives, reverting to Robot Mode and landing in front of him, bringing out her flamethrower and laser gun, and fires at the autogun, as the missile comes closer...
